96
00:05:51,260 --> 00:05:52,300
So did you.

97
00:05:52,300 --> 00:05:53,020
Right?

98
00:05:54,580 --> 00:05:57,140
As long as we tried,
there’s a lesson learned.

99
00:05:57,740 --> 00:05:59,100
All the frustrations are temporary.

100
