174
00:09:37,940 --> 00:09:38,980
You bought books there.

175
00:09:39,460 --> 00:09:40,180
Yeah.

176
00:09:42,780 --> 00:09:44,060
I came alone.

177
00:09:45,420 --> 00:09:47,580
