276
00:12:17,580 --> 00:12:19,460
We’ve been not only
to the market together,

277
00:12:19,460 --> 00:12:20,620
but also to the aquatic product market

278
00:12:20,620 --> 00:12:22,020
and drysaltery.

279
00:12:22,020 --> 00:12:24,420
